{
  "texts": [
    "To refine this large dataset, 40,500 duplicate entries were removed using automated tools, 10,500 records were marked as ineligible by these tools, and an additional 2000 records were removed for other reasons (see Fig. 2).",
    "This process reduced the pool to 64,000 documents, from which 26,000 records were excluded after further screening.",
    "Consequently, 38,000 reports were sought for retrieval, but 10,200 were not retrieved, leaving 27,800 reports to be assessed for eligibility.",
    "Of these, 10,000 reports were excluded due to the lack of relevant projects, 8869 were excluded for not being conducted within China, and 8900 were excluded because they did not involve K-12 teachers, a specific study population criterion.",
    "Ultimately, 31 studies were included in the final review after considering all the criteria and adding nine more relevant studies to ensure comprehensive topic coverage."
  ]
}